events.description:
Wanna make that idea into a piece of wall art? Create a poster size print using TeenHQ MakerSpace’s HP DesignJet Studio, 36” Printer. Each participant can create one 24”x36” poster to take home per month.&nbsp; 
  For images found online, ensure they are "large" enough for good print quality. Look for images that are at a minimum of 2,000 x 2,000 px.  Create a collage of images or add effects on Canva. Be sure your canvas size is 24in x 36in.  
 This program is free. No pre-registration required
